{"tid":688271,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"pizza-box真係垃圾黎","createTime":"2018-06-03T05:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T21:54:57.000Z","uid":73803,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8872683576d5a8855e55a6c5c357f10872ecd99c","tid":688271,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"送外賣會送留野都間間豪餐廳都會，都習慣晒<br />\n<br />\n咁我網上落單，落單成功之後會有個短信黎話比你聽，話你落單成功有咩查詢可以打比比佢地<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/133928_f185fb56f12e9981ca716c7c14949f4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F133928_f185fb56f12e9981ca716c7c14949f4a.png&h=51453222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知一打過去<br />\n係留言信箱，話咩好快回覆你<br />\n<br />\n咁我睇返張單，諗住打個去鋪頭問，點知個電話又係一鳩樣，又係留言信箱<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/134123_9605e07906873ada4f890c193c532430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F134123_9605e07906873ada4f890c193c532430.png&h=c62dccf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係我出post前一刻<br />\n我仲未打通電話或者佢哋有人搵返我<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/134306_fd51f49c8d562b6b0b1e541949cf924e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F134306_fd51f49c8d562b6b0b1e541949cf924e.png&h=4551b07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我希望各位巴打引以為鑑，下次買pizza請三思，諗下有冇其他餐廳叫<br />\n<br />\n因為佢哋真係會覆返你電話"},{"pid":"96b9a9054dac0d97a0ab0308699575ba0b64804b","tid":688271,"uid":151664,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/135218_6120e59a1381355ad2d3d0f60878cac9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F135218_6120e59a1381355ad2d3d0f60878cac9.png&h=9075a8ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你蠢到豬咁